{
  "stem": "5328.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In the middle of the night at-- at 3 o'clock in the morning, we heard shooting, guns shooting, as they shot right into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we already knew what's going on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Everybody was out of the houses.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "With nightgowns, with pajamas, naked, and start running from one place to another to rescue, to run out from the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Whoever was killed was killed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I mean, they're shooting.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Whoever was killed right on the spot.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We were running like over dead bodies.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I myself was running over dead bodies.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I didn't-- it didn't even look like it's a corpse.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It didn't matter.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It didn't matter, you know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Everybody wanted survive.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "My mother hold-- hold my younger sister and myself both hands.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Because we were the youngest children.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And at once, my mother disappeared.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I didn't see her anyone, and I was all by myself.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My younger sister and myself holding us by hands.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and one moment, I lost my mother.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my sister.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was by myself.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[SIGHS] And the border of the ghetto was-- on the other side of the ghetto was a house, big house, with a basement.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I saw people are pushing theirself into that basement.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I went to and I had my half a body was already in the basement.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So somebody from the inside pushed me out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I said to myself, oh, how selfish they are.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In a moment like that, who cares how-- how many people are they?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Just let me in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they pushed me out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I pushed myself in again.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They pushed me out again.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I went-- left that basement, and I went into a-- [SIGHS] to-- what is [NON-ENGLISH]?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Where-- in a--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Farm.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
